name: Mild Zinc Plated Full Extension Super Heavy Duty Slide 1150mm DZ4180-080-035-0115U
description:
Zinc-plated super heavy duty slide DZ4180-080-035-U, in a slide length of up to 2000mm and a slide profile height of 80mm

Accuride stock an impressive range of heavy duty products, however the super heavy duty DZ4180-080-035-U telescopic slide has taken this range to the next level.

Designed with an I-beam intermediate member for extra strength, the DZ4180-080-035-U telescopic slide is able to support up to 980kg, even when at full extension.

If you are looking for a heavy duty slide which can support weights of up to 980kg whilst maintaining a smooth and stable movement, then this is the slide for you.

It is common within the industry to use mild steel balls with a diameter of 8mm or less. However, to achieve a smooth and controlled slide movement whilst still supporting such a large weight, the DZ4180-080-035-U uses stainless steel ball with a diameter of 10mm.

Threaded mounting holes also allow for additional stability and simple mounting using the customers’ preferred bolt type.

The mild zinc plated slide has an 80mm profile height and can be ordered in a range of lengths of up to 2000mm, and can function in temperatures between -20°C to +110°C.

This, along with the ability to support such an impressive weight, makes the mild zinc-plated slide suitable for use in a range of mobile and stationary applications from industrial storage to automation and robotics.

The full extension feature makes the product especially well suited to supporting subunits like chillers, filters or motors as it allows for full and easy access to the back of the compartment for easy maintenance or cleaning.

The slide is not limited to battery compartments in railways and electric cars or unloading ammunition in military vehicles. The slide can also help to position heavy components precisely for picking and handling by robots in smart factories.

Customisation

The impressive 4180-080-035-U series is available in either zinc or stainless steel finishes, and can be customised to fit your requirements, with a range of extension options and slide lengths of up to 2000mm possible.

Our technical consulting ability means that our experienced team of engineers can work directly with you to customize the product to your needs.

If you are interested in a customized version of the super heavy duty DZ4180-080-035-U slide contact us directly.

name: Mild Zinc Plated Full Extension Super Heavy Duty Slide 1250mm DZ4180-080-035-0125U
description:
Zinc-plated super heavy duty slide DZ4180-080-035-U, in a slide length of up to 2000mm and a slide profile height of 80mm

Accuride stock an impressive range of heavy duty products, however the super heavy duty DZ4180-080-035-U telescopic slide has taken this range to the next level.

Designed with an I-beam intermediate member for extra strength, the DZ4180-080-035-U telescopic slide is able to support up to 980kg, even when at full extension.

If you are looking for a heavy duty slide which can support weights of up to 980kg whilst maintaining a smooth and stable movement, then this is the slide for you.

It is common within the industry to use mild steel balls with a diameter of 8mm or less. However, to achieve a smooth and controlled slide movement whilst still supporting such a large weight, the DZ4180-080-035-U uses stainless steel ball with a diameter of 10mm.

Threaded mounting holes also allow for additional stability and simple mounting using the customers’ preferred bolt type.

The mild zinc plated slide has an 80mm profile height and can be ordered in a range of lengths of up to 2000mm, and can function in temperatures between -20°C to +110°C.

This, along with the ability to support such an impressive weight, makes the mild zinc-plated slide suitable for use in a range of mobile and stationary applications from industrial storage to automation and robotics.

The full extension feature makes the product especially well suited to supporting subunits like chillers, filters or motors as it allows for full and easy access to the back of the compartment for easy maintenance or cleaning.

The slide is not limited to battery compartments in railways and electric cars or unloading ammunition in military vehicles. The slide can also help to position heavy components precisely for picking and handling by robots in smart factories.

Customisation

The impressive 4180-080-035-U series is available in either zinc or stainless steel finishes, and can be customised to fit your requirements, with a range of extension options and slide lengths of up to 2000mm possible.

Our technical consulting ability means that our experienced team of engineers can work directly with you to customize the product to your needs.

If you are interested in a customized version of the super heavy duty DZ4180-080-035-U slide contact us directly.
short_description:
The DZ4180-080-035-U full extension super heavy duty slide comes in a slide length of up to 2000mm and can support up to 980kg.

Designed with an I-Beam intermediate member for improved strength and 10mm diameter stainless steel balls for a smoother movement, the DZ4180-080-035-U telescopic slide is well suited to the industrial storage, transport and automation industries.
product_features:
• Super heavy duty slide with a load rating of up to 980kg
  • 100% extension, allowing for easy access to the back of storage compartments
  • 10mm ball bearing diameter for smooth running and stability, compared to the industry standard of 8mm
  • Double-T intermediate member for extra strength
  • Threaded mounting holes for additional stability
  • Flat mounting not recommended, for queries speak to tech support
  • Corrosion resistant zinc plated finish, subject to 12 hours salt spray testing
  • Designed for a range of mobile and stationary applications:
    • battery tray access for electric, emergency services, military and mining vehiceles
    • automation and robotics
    • industrial storage

name: Mild Zinc Plated Full Extension Super Heavy Duty Slide 1500mm DZ4180-080-035-0150U
description:
Zinc-plated super heavy duty slide DZ4180-080-035-U, in a slide length of up to 2000mm and a slide profile height of 80mm

Accuride stock an impressive range of heavy duty products, however the super heavy duty DZ4180-080-035-U telescopic slide has taken this range to the next level.

Designed with an I-beam intermediate member for extra strength, the DZ4180-080-035-U telescopic slide is able to support up to 980kg, even when at full extension.

If you are looking for a heavy duty slide which can support weights of up to 980kg whilst maintaining a smooth and stable movement, then this is the slide for you.

It is common within the industry to use mild steel balls with a diameter of 8mm or less. However, to achieve a smooth and controlled slide movement whilst still supporting such a large weight, the DZ4180-080-035-U uses stainless steel ball with a diameter of 10mm.

Threaded mounting holes also allow for additional stability and simple mounting using the customers’ preferred bolt type.

The mild zinc plated slide has an 80mm profile height and can be ordered in a range of lengths of up to 2000mm, and can function in temperatures between -20°C to +110°C.

This, along with the ability to support such an impressive weight, makes the mild zinc-plated slide suitable for use in a range of mobile and stationary applications from industrial storage to automation and robotics.

The full extension feature makes the product especially well suited to supporting subunits like chillers, filters or motors as it allows for full and easy access to the back of the compartment for easy maintenance or cleaning.

The slide is not limited to battery compartments in railways and electric cars or unloading ammunition in military vehicles. The slide can also help to position heavy components precisely for picking and handling by robots in smart factories.

Customisation

The impressive 4180-080-035-U series is available in either zinc or stainless steel finishes, and can be customised to fit your requirements, with a range of extension options and slide lengths of up to 2000mm possible.

Our technical consulting ability means that our experienced team of engineers can work directly with you to customize the product to your needs.

If you are interested in a customized version of the super heavy duty DZ4180-080-035-U slide contact us directly.
short_description:
The DZ4180-080-035-U full extension super heavy duty slide comes in a slide length of up to 2000mm and can support up to 980kg.

Designed with an I-Beam intermediate member for improved strength and 10mm diameter stainless steel balls for a smoother movement, the DZ4180-080-035-U telescopic slide is well suited to the industrial storage, transport and automation industries.
product_features:
• Super heavy duty slide with a load rating of up to 980kg
  • 100% extension, allowing for easy access to the back of storage compartments
  • 10mm ball bearing diameter for smooth running and stability, compared to the industry standard of 8mm
  • Double-T intermediate member for extra strength
  • Threaded mounting holes for additional stability
  • Flat mounting not recommended, for queries speak to tech support
  • Corrosion resistant zinc plated finish, subject to 12 hours salt spray testing
  • Designed for a range of mobile and stationary applications:
    • battery tray access for electric, emergency services, military and mining vehiceles
    • automation and robotics
    • industrial storage

Accuride stock an impressive range of heavy duty products, however the super heavy duty DZ4180-080-035-U telescopic slide has taken this range to the next level.

Designed with an I-beam intermediate member for extra strength, the DZ4180-080-035-U telescopic slide is able to support up to 980kg, even when at full extension.

If you are looking for a heavy duty slide which can support weights of up to 980kg whilst maintaining a smooth and stable movement, then this is the slide for you.

It is common within the industry to use mild steel balls with a diameter of 8mm or less. However, to achieve a smooth and controlled slide movement whilst still supporting such a large weight, the DZ4180-080-035-U uses stainless steel ball with a diameter of 10mm.

Threaded mounting holes also allow for additional stability and simple mounting using the customers’ preferred bolt type.

The mild zinc plated slide has an 80mm profile height and can be ordered in a range of lengths of up to 2000mm, and can function in temperatures between -20°C to +110°C.

This, along with the ability to support such an impressive weight, makes the mild zinc-plated slide suitable for use in a range of mobile and stationary applications from industrial storage to automation and robotics.

The full extension feature makes the product especially well suited to supporting subunits like chillers, filters or motors as it allows for full and easy access to the back of the compartment for easy maintenance or cleaning.

The slide is not limited to battery compartments in railways and electric cars or unloading ammunition in military vehicles. The slide can also help to position heavy components precisely for picking and handling by robots in smart factories.

Customisation

The impressive 4180-080-035-U series is available in either zinc or stainless steel finishes, and can be customised to fit your requirements, with a range of extension options and slide lengths of up to 2000mm possible.

Our technical consulting ability means that our experienced team of engineers can work directly with you to customize the product to your needs.

If you are interested in a customized version of the super heavy duty DZ4180-080-035-U slide contact us directly.
short_description:
The DZ4180-080-035-U full extension super heavy duty slide comes in a slide length of up to 2000mm and can support up to 980kg.

Designed with an I-Beam intermediate member for improved strength and 10mm diameter stainless steel balls for a smoother movement, the DZ4180-080-035-U telescopic slide is well suited to the industrial storage, transport and automation industries.
product_features:
• Super heavy duty slide with a load rating of up to 980kg
  • 100% extension, allowing for easy access to the back of storage compartments
  • 10mm ball bearing diameter for smooth running and stability, compared to the industry standard of 8mm
  • Double-T intermediate member for extra strength
  • Threaded mounting holes for additional stability
  • Flat mounting not recommended, for queries speak to tech support
  • Corrosion resistant zinc plated finish, subject to 12 hours salt spray testing
  • Designed for a range of mobile and stationary applications:
    • battery tray access for electric, emergency services, military and mining vehiceles
    • automation and robotics
    • industrial storage

name: Mild Zinc Plated Full Extension Super Heavy Duty Slide 1750mm DZ4180-080-035-0175U
description:
Zinc-plated super heavy duty slide DZ4180-080-035-U, in a slide length of up to 2000mm and a slide profile height of 80mm

Accuride stock an impressive range of heavy duty products, however the super heavy duty DZ4180-080-035-U telescopic slide has taken this range to the next level.

Designed with an I-beam intermediate member for extra strength, the DZ4180-080-035-U telescopic slide is able to support up to 980kg, even when at full extension.

If you are looking for a heavy duty slide which can support weights of up to 980kg whilst maintaining a smooth and stable movement, then this is the slide for you.

It is common within the industry to use mild steel balls with a diameter of 8mm or less. However, to achieve a smooth and controlled slide movement whilst still supporting such a large weight, the DZ4180-080-035-U uses stainless steel ball with a diameter of 10mm.

Threaded mounting holes also allow for additional stability and simple mounting using the customers’ preferred bolt type.

The mild zinc plated slide has an 80mm profile height and can be ordered in a range of lengths of up to 2000mm, and can function in temperatures between -20°C to +110°C.

This, along with the ability to support such an impressive weight, makes the mild zinc-plated slide suitable for use in a range of mobile and stationary applications from industrial storage to automation and robotics.

The full extension feature makes the product especially well suited to supporting subunits like chillers, filters or motors as it allows for full and easy access to the back of the compartment for easy maintenance or cleaning.

The slide is not limited to battery compartments in railways and electric cars or unloading ammunition in military vehicles. The slide can also help to position heavy components precisely for picking and handling by robots in smart factories.

Customisation

The impressive 4180-080-035-U series is available in either zinc or stainless steel finishes, and can be customised to fit your requirements, with a range of extension options and slide lengths of up to 2000mm possible.

Our technical consulting ability means that our experienced team of engineers can work directly with you to customize the product to your needs.

If you are interested in a customized version of the super heavy duty DZ4180-080-035-U slide contact us directly.
short_description:
The DZ4180-080-035-U full extension super heavy duty slide comes in a slide length of up to 2000mm and can support up to 980kg.

Designed with an I-Beam intermediate member for improved strength and 10mm diameter stainless steel balls for a smoother movement, the DZ4180-080-035-U telescopic slide is well suited to the industrial storage, transport and automation industries.
product_features:
• Super heavy duty slide with a load rating of up to 980kg
  • 100% extension, allowing for easy access to the back of storage compartments
  • 10mm ball bearing diameter for smooth running and stability, compared to the industry standard of 8mm
  • Double-T intermediate member for extra strength
  • Threaded mounting holes for additional stability
  • Flat mounting not recommended, for queries speak to tech support
  • Corrosion resistant zinc plated finish, subject to 12 hours salt spray testing
  • Designed for a range of mobile and stationary applications:
    • battery tray access for electric, emergency services, military and mining vehiceles
    • automation and robotics
    • industrial storage

name: Mild Zinc Plated Full Extension Super Heavy Duty Slide 1850mm DZ4180-080-035-0185U
description:
Zinc-plated super heavy duty slide DZ4180-080-035-U, in a slide length of up to 2000mm and a slide profile height of 80mm

Accuride stock an impressive range of heavy duty products, however the super heavy duty DZ4180-080-035-U telescopic slide has taken this range to the next level.

Designed with an I-beam intermediate member for extra strength, the DZ4180-080-035-U telescopic slide is able to support up to 980kg, even when at full extension.

If you are looking for a heavy duty slide which can support weights of up to 980kg whilst maintaining a smooth and stable movement, then this is the slide for you.

It is common within the industry to use mild steel balls with a diameter of 8mm or less. However, to achieve a smooth and controlled slide movement whilst still supporting such a large weight, the DZ4180-080-035-U uses stainless steel ball with a diameter of 10mm.

Threaded mounting holes also allow for additional stability and simple mounting using the customers’ preferred bolt type.

The mild zinc plated slide has an 80mm profile height and can be ordered in a range of lengths of up to 2000mm, and can function in temperatures between -20°C to +110°C.

This, along with the ability to support such an impressive weight, makes the mild zinc-plated slide suitable for use in a range of mobile and stationary applications from industrial storage to automation and robotics.

The full extension feature makes the product especially well suited to supporting subunits like chillers, filters or motors as it allows for full and easy access to the back of the compartment for easy maintenance or cleaning.

The slide is not limited to battery compartments in railways and electric cars or unloading ammunition in military vehicles. The slide can also help to position heavy components precisely for picking and handling by robots in smart factories.

Customisation

The impressive 4180-080-035-U series is available in either zinc or stainless steel finishes, and can be customised to fit your requirements, with a range of extension options and slide lengths of up to 2000mm possible.

Our technical consulting ability means that our experienced team of engineers can work directly with you to customize the product to your needs.

If you are interested in a customized version of the super heavy duty DZ4180-080-035-U slide contact us directly.

name: Mild Zinc Plated Full Extension Super Heavy Duty Slide 2000mm DZ4180-080-035-0200U
description:
Zinc-plated super heavy duty slide DZ4180-080-035-U, in a slide length of up to 2000mm and a slide profile height of 80mm

Accuride stock an impressive range of heavy duty products, however the super heavy duty DZ4180-080-035-U telescopic slide has taken this range to the next level.

Designed with an I-beam intermediate member for extra strength, the DZ4180-080-035-U telescopic slide is able to support up to 980kg, even when at full extension.

If you are looking for a heavy duty slide which can support weights of up to 980kg whilst maintaining a smooth and stable movement, then this is the slide for you.

It is common within the industry to use mild steel balls with a diameter of 8mm or less. However, to achieve a smooth and controlled slide movement whilst still supporting such a large weight, the DZ4180-080-035-U uses stainless steel ball with a diameter of 10mm.

Threaded mounting holes also allow for additional stability and simple mounting using the customers’ preferred bolt type.

The mild zinc plated slide has an 80mm profile height and can be ordered in a range of lengths of up to 2000mm, and can function in temperatures between -20°C to +110°C.

This, along with the ability to support such an impressive weight, makes the mild zinc-plated slide suitable for use in a range of mobile and stationary applications from industrial storage to automation and robotics.

The full extension feature makes the product especially well suited to supporting subunits like chillers, filters or motors as it allows for full and easy access to the back of the compartment for easy maintenance or cleaning.

The slide is not limited to battery compartments in railways and electric cars or unloading ammunition in military vehicles. The slide can also help to position heavy components precisely for picking and handling by robots in smart factories.

Customisation

The impressive 4180-080-035-U series is available in either zinc or stainless steel finishes, and can be customised to fit your requirements, with a range of extension options and slide lengths of up to 2000mm possible.

Our technical consulting ability means that our experienced team of engineers can work directly with you to customize the product to your needs.

If you are interested in a customized version of the super heavy duty DZ4180-080-035-U slide contact us directly.
short_description:
The DZ4180-080-035-U full extension super heavy duty slide comes in a slide length of up to 2000mm and can support up to 980kg.

Designed with an I-Beam intermediate member for improved strength and 10mm diameter stainless steel balls for a smoother movement, the DZ4180-080-035-U telescopic slide is well suited to the industrial storage, transport and automation industries.
product_features:
• Super heavy duty slide with a load rating of up to 980kg
  • 100% extension, allowing for easy access to the back of storage compartments
  • 10mm ball bearing diameter for smooth running and stability, compared to the industry standard of 8mm
  • Double-T intermediate member for extra strength
  • Threaded mounting holes for additional stability
  • Flat mounting not recommended, for queries speak to tech support
  • Corrosion resistant zinc plated finish, subject to 12 hours salt spray testing
  • Designed for a range of mobile and stationary applications:
    • battery tray access for electric, emergency services, military and mining vehiceles
    • automation and robotics
    • industrial storage

The DS5321EC stainless steel easy-close slide is designed to support loads of up to 100 kg, making it suitable for a range of heavy-duty applications. The slide is made of corrosion resistant materials and can withstand temperatures of between 0 °C to 40 °C, making the slide especially well suited to professional kitchen and food service environments.

Suitable for wide drawers

Suitable for drawers up to 1000mm wide, this is a smooth piece of motion hardware for heavy-duty drawers, trays and shelves in commercial, industrial and residential spaces.

Full extension slide for easy access

Easy close feature

The easy-close mechanism, also known as “soft-close”, has been engineered to be integrated into the slide for optimal function and design. This allows the slide to close slowly and softly, making it more pleasant for sound-sensitive environments such as hospitals and also safer for domestic applications such as kitchen drawers, as the smooth and soft closing minimizes the force of the drawer if fingers got trapped.

An optional bracket accessory kit is available for various mounting options.

This allows the slide to close slowly and softly, making it more pleasant for sound-sensitive environments such as hospitals and also safer for domestic applications such as kitchen drawers, as the smooth and soft closing minimizes the force of the drawer if fingers got trapped.

An optional bracket accessory kit is available for various mounting options.

name: Stainless Steel Full Extension Telescopic Slide DS2330-0015DL
description:
The Full Extension Slide DS2330DL - Durable Stainless Steel Slide for Extreme Environments

The Full Extension Stainless Steel Slide DS2330DL has been designed for applications subject to corrosion and extreme temperatures. Having been rigorously tested to ten thousand cycles, each pair of stainless steel DS2330DL slides can support a load capacity of up to 15kg.

Compact Design for Tight Spaces:

With a slide thickness of 19.5mm and a slide height of only 23mm, the compact design of the DS2330DL slide makes it suitable for confined spaces such as small warming drawer compartments or trays beneath fireplaces, optimising functionality without compromising space.

Flat Mounting Capability:

While suitable for flat mounting, it is important to note that this configuration reduces the load rating by 75%.

Applications:

  • Food Safe Environments: Engineered for use in food environments, this slide can withstand extreme temperatures ranging from -80°C to +500°C, making it ideal for food applications subject to both extreme heat and cold environments. To ensure compliance with stringent food safety standards, the DS2330DL telescopic slide has been made using food safe materials.
  • High-Temperature Ovens for Food Preparation: Ideal for harsh environments, this durable stainless steel slide operates seamlessly in temperatures up to +500°C, catering to applications like pizza ovens, stone ovens, steak grills, and charcoal ovens.
  • Industrial Processes: Able to reliably function in industrial processes operating at temperatures up to +500°C, such as heat treatment, coating, and curing applications.
  • Very Low Temperature Applications: Exceptionally versatile, the DS2330DL slide is capable of functioning in temperatures as low as -80°C. Unlike most other slides which use grease that cannot withstand temperatures of below -40 °C or -50 °C, the DS2330DL slide can function in these cold environments, making the DS2330DL slide suitable for use in industrial or laboratory refrigerators.
  • Frequent Cleaning: Safe to use in applications that require frequent cleaning, unlike other slides, where the grease will be washed out over time when cleaning an application with pressurised water. The self-lubricating mechanism of the DS2330DL slide, facilitated by graphite balls, ensures consistent performance even in demanding cleaning processes commonly used in the food and medical industries.

For further details, refer to the datasheet or contact us directly and one of our technical experts will be happy to help.
short_description: Stainless steel full extension telescopic slide DS2330DL, with a load rating up to 15kg, slide thickness of 19.5mm and slide height of 23mm. Ideal for environments subject to corrosion or extreme temperatures, like high temperature ovens, furnaces and industrial refrigeration.
product_features:
• Light-duty slide, able to support applications of up to 15kg
  • 100% full extension allows for easy access to the back of the drawer or application
  • Slide thickness of 19.5mm, making the low profile slide suitable for small spaces.
  • High-grade stainless-steel slide suitable for applications subject to corrosion
  • Able to function in temperatures of between -80 °C to +500 °C, making the slide suitable for refrigerators, ovens and high temperature industrial processing applications.
  • Made using food safe materials, ensuring that the slide meets food safety standards

With a slide thickness of 19.5mm and a slide height of only 23mm, the compact design of the DS2330DL slide makes it suitable for confined spaces such as small warming drawer compartments or trays beneath fireplaces, optimising functionality without compromising space.

Flat Mounting Capability:

While suitable for flat mounting, it is important to note that this configuration reduces the load rating by 75%.

Applications:

  • Food Safe Environments: Engineered for use in food environments, this slide can withstand extreme temperatures ranging from -80°C to +500°C, making it ideal for food applications subject to both extreme heat and cold environments. To ensure compliance with stringent food safety standards, the DS2330DL telescopic slide has been made using food safe materials.
  • High-Temperature Ovens for Food Preparation: Ideal for harsh environments, this durable stainless steel slide operates seamlessly in temperatures up to +500°C, catering to applications like pizza ovens, stone ovens, steak grills, and charcoal ovens.
  • Industrial Processes: Able to reliably function in industrial processes operating at temperatures up to +500°C, such as heat treatment, coating, and curing applications.
  • Very Low Temperature Applications: Exceptionally versatile, the DS2330DL slide is capable of functioning in temperatures as low as -80°C. Unlike most other slides which use grease that cannot withstand temperatures of below -40 °C or -50 °C, the DS2330DL slide can function in these cold environments, making the DS2330DL slide suitable for use in industrial or laboratory refrigerators.
  • Frequent Cleaning: Safe to use in applications that require frequent cleaning, unlike other slides, where the grease will be washed out over time when cleaning an application with pressurised water. The self-lubricating mechanism of the DS2330DL slide, facilitated by graphite balls, ensures consistent performance even in demanding cleaning processes commonly used in the food and medical industries.

For further details, refer to the datasheet or contact us directly and one of our technical experts will be happy to help.

name: Light Duty Linear Track System LA1815-0020
description:
The LA1815 Light Duty Linear Track System: Precise movement for small machine doors, assembly fixtures and simple XY tables

Introducing the LA1815 light duty linear track system, designed for handling loads of up to 8.2kg (static) and up to 3.1kg (dynamic) with precision and durability. The LA1815 linear track system includes an aluminum track, steel plate, and end stops. The linear track system moves with precision, making it ideal for a variety of applications.

Industrial Applications

From small machine doors and hatches to assembly fixtures that help moving a workpiece during an assembly operation, or covers for bins to guide an operator to use the right items P oka-yoke , the LA1815 linear guide offers smooth and controlled movement, ensuring efficient operation in industrial settings.

Small Cabinets

The LA1815 linear track is perfect for small cabinet display units like shop counter displays.

XY Tables

The LA1815 linear slide is designed for use in simple XY tables, providing a sturdy foundation for various positioning tasks. This application is possible due to the ability to flat mount the slide.

Retail Counters

The LA1815 is also a popular addition for commercial spaces, such as beauty counters in retail environments. This enhances the user experience as the added movement makes it more interactive for the customer as well as making it easier to rearrange the display stand.

The LA1815 light duty linear track system brings precise movement to a range of applications, from enhancing productivity on the factory floor to elevating the aesthetics of retail displays.

For more information, take a look at the product datasheet or contact us directly.
short_description:
Light duty linear track system LA1815 designed for applications such as small machine doors, assembly fixtures and simple XY tables.

Max Load Rating (Static): 8.2 kg
Max Load Rating (Dynamic): 3.1 kg

  • Precise linear motion through the full travel

name: Light Duty Linear Track System LA1815-0060
description:
The LA1815 Light Duty Linear Track System: Precise movement for small machine doors, assembly fixtures and simple XY tables

Introducing the LA1815 light duty linear track system, designed for handling loads of up to 8.2kg (static) and up to 3.1kg (dynamic) with precision and durability. The LA1815 linear track system includes an aluminum track, steel plate, and end stops. The linear track system moves with precision, making it ideal for a variety of applications.

Industrial Applications

From small machine doors and hatches to assembly fixtures that help moving a workpiece during an assembly operation, or covers for bins to guide an operator to use the right items P oka-yoke , the LA1815 linear guide offers smooth and controlled movement, ensuring efficient operation in industrial settings.

Small Cabinets

The LA1815 linear track is perfect for small cabinet display units like shop counter displays.

XY Tables

The LA1815 linear slide is designed for use in simple XY tables, providing a sturdy foundation for various positioning tasks. This application is possible due to the ability to flat mount the slide.

Retail Counters

The LA1815 is also a popular addition for commercial spaces, such as beauty counters in retail environments. This enhances the user experience as the added movement makes it more interactive for the customer as well as making it easier to rearrange the display stand.

The LA1815 light duty linear track system brings precise movement to a range of applications, from enhancing productivity on the factory floor to elevating the aesthetics of retail displays.

For more information, take a look at the product datasheet or contact us directly.

name: Soft Close Drawer Slide DZ3832-0035EC-D
description:
Upgrade Your Application with the Improved Soft Close Drawer Slide DZ3832-EC-D

Robust Load Capacity and Full Extension

The Soft Close Drawer Slide DZ3832-EC-D can handle loads of up to 45 kg, making it perfect for both light and medium-duty applications. With its 100% slide extension feature, you'll have full access to the entire drawer, maximising storage and ease of use.

Durable Construction and Compact Design

Constructed from mild steel with a bright zinc finish, this drawer slide is designed for strength and durability. The 12.7 mm thickness makes the slide compact enough to fit into small spaces without compromising on your cabinetry's overall design and functionality.

DZ3832-EC-D Slide Features

The DZ3832-EC-D telescopic slide comes equipped with a soft close mechanism to prevent drawer slamming, enhancing both the lifespan of your drawers and the overall user experience. Additional features include front disconnect for easy removal and cam drawer adjust for precise alignment.

Easy Installation and Versatile Use

Designed for vertical side mounting only, the DZ3832-EC-D drawer slide is easy to install using M4 screws, 4mm wood screws, or 6mm Euro screws. Please note that it is not suitable for flat mounting.

Tested for Reliability

This drawer slide has undergone 12 hours of salt spray testing and operates effectively in temperatures ranging from 10 °C to 40 °C, making it a reliable choice for indoor environments.

Upgrade your cabinetry with the Soft Close Drawer Slide DZ3832-EC-D. Take a look at the product datasheet or contact us directly for more information.

A durable slide with a load capacity of up to 45 kg

Experience exceptional durability with the DZ4501 Full Extension Slide with Disconnect. Sold as a pair, the telescopic slides are crafted from high-quality mild steel with a bright zinc finish. Ultimate Accessibility

Enjoy ultimate accessibility with the DZ4501 slide's 100% full extension capability, allowing easy access to your entire drawer, even the items at the very back. Designed to fit seamlessly into compact spaces, it requires just 12.7 mm of side space, optimising storage efficiency.

Effortless Installation and Maintenance

Effortless installation and maintenance are made possible with the convenient disconnect feature, simplifying both processes. The DZ4501 slide is also equipped with breathing tabs, designed to facilitate straightforward installation, ensuring a perfect fit every time.

Rigorously Tested for Reliable Performance

The DZ4501 telescopic slide has been rigorously tested for reliable performance. The slide has undergone 12 hours of salt spray testing to withstand harsh environments and operates efficiently in temperatures ranging from -20 °C to 70 °C.

Hold-In Feature for Secure Closure

The hold-in feature keeps your drawers securely closed, preventing unwanted opening and ensuring stability and safety in various settings.

Versatile Applications Across Multiple Industries

The DZ4501 Full Extension Slide with Disconnect excels in a wide range of applications across different industries:

name: Full Extension Slide with Disconnect DZ4501-0025
description:
DZ4501 Full Extension Slide with Disconnect: Maximum Efficiency, Effortless Installation

A durable slide with a load capacity of up to 45 kg

Experience exceptional durability with the DZ4501 Full Extension Slide with Disconnect. Sold as a pair, the telescopic slides are crafted from high-quality mild steel with a bright zinc finish. Built to withstand the rigors of everyday use, the DZ4501 slide boasts an impressive load capacity of up to 45 kg. Its robust construction ensures long-lasting performance, making it ideal for various applications. The slide is available in lengths ranging from 150 mm to 900 mm, offering versatility for different needs.As a part of our BEE slide range, the slide combines durability and versatility to meet the needs of a wide range of applications.

Ultimate Accessibility

Enjoy ultimate accessibility with the DZ4501 slide's 100% full extension capability, allowing easy access to your entire drawer, even the items at the very back. Designed to fit seamlessly into compact spaces, it requires just 12.7 mm of side space, optimising storage efficiency.

Effortless Installation and Maintenance

Effortless installation and maintenance are made possible with the convenient disconnect feature, simplifying both processes. The DZ4501 slide is also equipped with breathing tabs, designed to facilitate straightforward installation, ensuring a perfect fit every time.

Rigorously Tested for Reliable Performance

The DZ4501 telescopic slide has been rigorously tested for reliable performance. The slide has undergone 12 hours of salt spray testing to withstand harsh environments and operates efficiently in temperatures ranging from -20 °C to 70 °C.

Hold-In Feature for Secure Closure

The hold-in feature keeps your drawers securely closed, preventing unwanted opening and ensuring stability and safety in various settings.

Versatile Applications Across Multiple Industries

The DZ4501 Full Extension Slide with Disconnect excels in a wide range of applications across different industries:

  • Interior Design and Home Renovations: Perfect for kitchen and bathroom drawers, the DZ4501 slide enhances accessibility and efficiency in residential settings, optimising storage solutions.
  • Light duty Commercial Settings: In office furniture and hotel receptions, the DZ4501 slide offers durability and ease of use, contributing to organized and functional spaces that cater to professional needs.
  • Light duty industrial applications: In industrial settings such as toolboxes, the DZ4501 slide ensures secure storage and easy access to tools and equipment, enhancing productivity and safety.

Upgrade your storage solutions across various industries with the DZ4501 Full Extension Slide with Disconnect. Designed for durability and versatility, it offers reliable performance and effortless installation in diverse applications.

name: Full Extension Slide with Disconnect DZ4501-0080
description:
DZ4501 Full Extension Slide with Disconnect: Maximum Efficiency, Effortless Installation

A durable slide with a load capacity of up to 45 kg

Experience exceptional durability with the DZ4501 Full Extension Slide with Disconnect. Sold as a pair, the telescopic slides are crafted from high-quality mild steel with a bright zinc finish. Built to withstand the rigors of everyday use, the DZ4501 slide boasts an impressive load capacity of up to 45 kg. Its robust construction ensures long-lasting performance, making it ideal for various applications. The slide is available in lengths ranging from 150 mm to 900 mm, offering versatility for different needs.As a part of our BEE slide range, the slide combines durability and versatility to meet the needs of a wide range of applications.

Ultimate Accessibility

Enjoy ultimate accessibility with the DZ4501 slide's 100% full extension capability, allowing easy access to your entire drawer, even the items at the very back. Designed to fit seamlessly into compact spaces, it requires just 12.7 mm of side space, optimising storage efficiency.

Effortless Installation and Maintenance

Effortless installation and maintenance are made possible with the convenient disconnect feature, simplifying both processes. The DZ4501 slide is also equipped with breathing tabs, designed to facilitate straightforward installation, ensuring a perfect fit every time.

Rigorously Tested for Reliable Performance

The DZ4501 telescopic slide has been rigorously tested for reliable performance. The slide has undergone 12 hours of salt spray testing to withstand harsh environments and operates efficiently in temperatures ranging from -20 °C to 70 °C.

Hold-In Feature for Secure Closure

The hold-in feature keeps your drawers securely closed, preventing unwanted opening and ensuring stability and safety in various settings.

Versatile Applications Across Multiple Industries

The DZ4501 Full Extension Slide with Disconnect excels in a wide range of applications across different industries:

  • Interior Design and Home Renovations: Perfect for kitchen and bathroom drawers, the DZ4501 slide enhances accessibility and efficiency in residential settings, optimising storage solutions.
  • Light duty Commercial Settings: In office furniture and hotel receptions, the DZ4501 slide offers durability and ease of use, contributing to organized and functional spaces that cater to professional needs.
  • Light duty industrial applications: In industrial settings such as toolboxes, the DZ4501 slide ensures secure storage and easy access to tools and equipment, enhancing productivity and safety.

Upgrade your storage solutions across various industries with the DZ4501 Full Extension Slide with Disconnect. Designed for durability and versatility, it offers reliable performance and effortless installation in diverse applications.

  • Breathing tabs for straightforward installation, ensuring a perfect fit every time.

name: Full Extension Slide with Touch Release DZ4501-0020TR
description:
Introducing the DZ4501-TR Full Extension Slide with Touch Release

The DZ4501-TR Full Extension Slide with Touch Release is a premium sliding solution designed for optimal performance and convenience. Constructed from mild steel with a bright zinc finish, this slide is sold as a pair and features a load rating of up to 35 kg. As a part of our BEE slide range, the slide combines durability and versatility to meet the needs of a wide range of applications.

Innovative Touch to Release Mechanism

One of the standout features of the DZ4501-TR telescopic slide is the touch to release (touch to open/ push to open) mechanism. This eliminates the need for handles, contributing to sleek and modern cabinetry designs. The push to open function offers seamless performance, ensuring that the drawer opens effortlessly with a simple touch.

Slide Installation

Key features of this slide include a disconnect mechanism that simplifies installation. Additionally, the DZ4501-TR slide is equipped with breathing tabs, designed to facilitate straightforward installation, ensuring a perfect fit every time.

Hold-in Feature

The hold-in feature guarantees that the drawer remains securely shut, enhancing safety and stability.

100% Extension Feature

Engineered to provide 100% full extension, the DZ4501-TR slide ensures easy access to the back of the drawer, making it perfect for a variety of applications.

For more information, contact us or download the product datasheet.

  • Push to open/ touch release function offers seamless performance, ensuring that the drawer opens effortlessly with a simple touch.
  • Accuride International Limited guarantees its “Quick Ship”™ slides against defects in material and workmanship. Please read more under quality and warranty policy section.

100% Extension Feature

name: Full Extension Slide with Easy Close DZ4501-0020EC
description:
Full Extension Slide with Easy Close DZ4501-EC: Your Answer to Quiet and Smooth Drawer Operation

Introducing the DZ4501-EC Full Extension Slide with Easy Close, designed to provide reliability and durability for various soft close applications. Engineered for 100% full extension, this slide offers easy access to previously unused drawer space, ensuring every inch of your storage is utilised efficiently. Available in slide lengths ranging from 200 mm to 600 mm, the DZ4501-EC caters to a range of applications. As a part of our BEE slide range, the slide combines durability and versatility to meet the needs of a wide range of applications.

Easy Close Mechanism:

The DZ4501-EC slide features an integrated easy close system (also known as ‘soft close’), eliminating loud slamming and ensuring a quiet, gentle closure. This makes it ideal for delicate equipment and noise-sensitive environments. With a load-bearing capacity of up to 35 kg, this slide guarantees smooth and reliable operation every time.

Full Extension Access:

Designed with a 100% full extension feature, the DZ4501-EC telescopic slide allows complete access to the entire drawer, making it perfect for storage spaces where reaching the back is important.

Easy Installation:

The front disconnect feature simplifies installation and maintenance, enabling easy detachment when necessary. Additionally, the slide is also equipped with breathing tabs, further facilitating a hassle-free setup.

Durability and Versatility

Constructed from mild steel, the DZ4501-EC easy close slide is built to last. It has been rigorously tested to function, ensuring smooth performance in various conditions.

Ideal Applications

The DZ4501-EC easy close slide is perfect for a wide range of applications, including:

  • Vending Machines: Ensures quiet and smooth operation, enhancing user experience.
  • Retail Storage: Provides secure and gentle closure, protecting delicate items.
  • Under Bed Storage Drawers: Maximises space utilisation with full extension and silent operation.

Upgrade your drawer systems with the DZ4501-EC easy close slide. Say goodbye to noisy drawers and welcome a new standard of silent, smooth performance.

name: Full Extension Slide with Easy Close DZ4501-0060EC
description:
Full Extension Slide with Easy Close DZ4501-EC: Your Answer to Quiet and Smooth Drawer Operation

Introducing the DZ4501-EC Full Extension Slide with Easy Close, designed to provide reliability and durability for various soft close applications. Engineered for 100% full extension, this slide offers easy access to previously unused drawer space, ensuring every inch of your storage is utilised efficiently. Available in slide lengths ranging from 200 mm to 600 mm, the DZ4501-EC caters to a range of applications. As a part of our BEE slide range, the slide combines durability and versatility to meet the needs of a wide range of applications.

Easy Close Mechanism:

The DZ4501-EC slide features an integrated easy close system (also known as ‘soft close’), eliminating loud slamming and ensuring a quiet, gentle closure. This makes it ideal for delicate equipment and noise-sensitive environments. With a load-bearing capacity of up to 35 kg, this slide guarantees smooth and reliable operation every time.

Full Extension Access:

Designed with a 100% full extension feature, the DZ4501-EC telescopic slide allows complete access to the entire drawer, making it perfect for storage spaces where reaching the back is important.

Easy Installation:

The front disconnect feature simplifies installation and maintenance, enabling easy detachment when necessary. Additionally, the slide is also equipped with breathing tabs, further facilitating a hassle-free setup.

Durability and Versatility

Constructed from mild steel, the DZ4501-EC easy close slide is built to last. It has been rigorously tested to function, ensuring smooth performance in various conditions.

Ideal Applications

The DZ4501-EC easy close slide is perfect for a wide range of applications, including:

  • Vending Machines: Ensures quiet and smooth operation, enhancing user experience.
  • Retail Storage: Provides secure and gentle closure, protecting delicate items.
  • Under Bed Storage Drawers: Maximises space utilisation with full extension and silent operation.

Upgrade your drawer systems with the DZ4501-EC easy close slide. Say goodbye to noisy drawers and welcome a new standard of silent, smooth performance.

name: Stainless Steel Full Extension Super Heavy Duty Slide DS4180-080-035-0050U
description:
Product Overview

The heavy-duty telescopic slide is a premium solution designed for applications requiring exceptional load-bearing capacity and reliability. Crafted entirely from stainless steel, it offers unparalleled durability and corrosion resistance, making it suitable for use in demanding environments. With a load rating of up to 825 kg per pair, the slide is engineered for strength without compromising performance. The slide provides 100% extension, allowing full access to the drawer or platform it supports, with a maximum deflection of just 1% at the rated load.

For optimal performance, the slide should be mounted vertically; flat mounting is not recommended as it reduces the load rating by 81%. The slide supports drawer widths of up to 3,000 mm, ensuring compatibility with a wide range of designs and requirements. It operates effectively across a broad temperature range of -20 °C to 300 °C, making it suitable for diverse environments, from refrigerated storage to high-heat industrial settings. Its permitted mounting orientations include vertical and flat mounts, though vertical mounting is strongly advised for maximum capacity.

Engineered with precision, this telescopic slide delivers exceptionally smooth movement and reliable operation in the most challenging conditions, ensuring long-term performance and minimal maintenance. Its robust stainless steel construction ensures resistance to wear, impact, and harsh conditions, making it a highly versatile choice.

Applications

This telescopic slide is designed to meet the rigorous demands of specialized industries where performance, durability, and hygiene are critical:

Medical Applications: The stainless steel construction and smooth operation make this slide ideal for medical environments, where reliability and cleanability are paramount. It is suitable for use in medical equipment, diagnostic devices, and storage solutions that require robust yet precise mechanisms.

Pharmaceutical Manufacturing: The slide’s corrosion-resistant design and high load capacity make it a perfect choice for pharmaceutical manufacturing environments. It ensures smooth and reliable operation in cleanrooms or production lines, maintaining efficiency and compliance with stringent industry standards.

Marine Applications: Designed to withstand harsh environments, this slide excels in marine settings, offering corrosion resistance in saltwater conditions. It is ideal for use in shipbuilding, offshore platforms, and storage systems exposed to the elements.

Military Applications: Built for extreme durability, the slide is well-suited for military use, including vehicle storage solutions, rugged equipment mounts, and other demanding applications where reliability and performance are critical under tough conditions.

This telescopic slide is a versatile, heavy-duty solution for industries requiring robust, high-performance sliding mechanisms. With its combination of strength, smoothness, and resilience, it delivers exceptional results in the most challenging environments.

name: Stainless Steel Full Extension Super Heavy Duty Slide DS4180-080-035-0075U
description:
Product Overview

The heavy-duty telescopic slide is a premium solution designed for applications requiring exceptional load-bearing capacity and reliability. Crafted entirely from stainless steel, it offers unparalleled durability and corrosion resistance, making it suitable for use in demanding environments. With a load rating of up to 825 kg per pair, the slide is engineered for strength without compromising performance. The slide provides 100% extension, allowing full access to the drawer or platform it supports, with a maximum deflection of just 1% at the rated load.

For optimal performance, the slide should be mounted vertically; flat mounting is not recommended as it reduces the load rating by 81%. The slide supports drawer widths of up to 3,000 mm, ensuring compatibility with a wide range of designs and requirements. It operates effectively across a broad temperature range of -20 °C to 300 °C, making it suitable for diverse environments, from refrigerated storage to high-heat industrial settings. Its permitted mounting orientations include vertical and flat mounts, though vertical mounting is strongly advised for maximum capacity.

Engineered with precision, this telescopic slide delivers exceptionally smooth movement and reliable operation in the most challenging conditions, ensuring long-term performance and minimal maintenance. Its robust stainless steel construction ensures resistance to wear, impact, and harsh conditions, making it a highly versatile choice.

Applications

This telescopic slide is designed to meet the rigorous demands of specialized industries where performance, durability, and hygiene are critical:

Medical Applications: The stainless steel construction and smooth operation make this slide ideal for medical environments, where reliability and cleanability are paramount. It is suitable for use in medical equipment, diagnostic devices, and storage solutions that require robust yet precise mechanisms.

Pharmaceutical Manufacturing: The slide’s corrosion-resistant design and high load capacity make it a perfect choice for pharmaceutical manufacturing environments. It ensures smooth and reliable operation in cleanrooms or production lines, maintaining efficiency and compliance with stringent industry standards.

Marine Applications: Designed to withstand harsh environments, this slide excels in marine settings, offering corrosion resistance in saltwater conditions. It is ideal for use in shipbuilding, offshore platforms, and storage systems exposed to the elements.

Military Applications: Built for extreme durability, the slide is well-suited for military use, including vehicle storage solutions, rugged equipment mounts, and other demanding applications where reliability and performance are critical under tough conditions.

This telescopic slide is a versatile, heavy-duty solution for industries requiring robust, high-performance sliding mechanisms. With its combination of strength, smoothness, and resilience, it delivers exceptional results in the most challenging environments.

With a remarkable load rating of up to 825 kg, it ensures reliable support for demanding applications while delivering smooth, precise movement. Ideal for industrial and professional use.

name: Stainless Steel Full Extension Super Heavy Duty Slide DS4180-080-035-0090U
description:
Product Overview

The heavy-duty telescopic slide is a premium solution designed for applications requiring exceptional load-bearing capacity and reliability. Crafted entirely from stainless steel, it offers unparalleled durability and corrosion resistance, making it suitable for use in demanding environments. With a load rating of up to 825 kg per pair, the slide is engineered for strength without compromising performance. The slide provides 100% extension, allowing full access to the drawer or platform it supports, with a maximum deflection of just 1% at the rated load.

For optimal performance, the slide should be mounted vertically; flat mounting is not recommended as it reduces the load rating by 81%. The slide supports drawer widths of up to 3,000 mm, ensuring compatibility with a wide range of designs and requirements. It operates effectively across a broad temperature range of -20 °C to 300 °C, making it suitable for diverse environments, from refrigerated storage to high-heat industrial settings. Its permitted mounting orientations include vertical and flat mounts, though vertical mounting is strongly advised for maximum capacity.

Engineered with precision, this telescopic slide delivers exceptionally smooth movement and reliable operation in the most challenging conditions, ensuring long-term performance and minimal maintenance. Its robust stainless steel construction ensures resistance to wear, impact, and harsh conditions, making it a highly versatile choice.

Applications

This telescopic slide is designed to meet the rigorous demands of specialized industries where performance, durability, and hygiene are critical:

Medical Applications: The stainless steel construction and smooth operation make this slide ideal for medical environments, where reliability and cleanability are paramount. It is suitable for use in medical equipment, diagnostic devices, and storage solutions that require robust yet precise mechanisms.

Pharmaceutical Manufacturing: The slide’s corrosion-resistant design and high load capacity make it a perfect choice for pharmaceutical manufacturing environments. It ensures smooth and reliable operation in cleanrooms or production lines, maintaining efficiency and compliance with stringent industry standards.

Marine Applications: Designed to withstand harsh environments, this slide excels in marine settings, offering corrosion resistance in saltwater conditions. It is ideal for use in shipbuilding, offshore platforms, and storage systems exposed to the elements.

Military Applications: Built for extreme durability, the slide is well-suited for military use, including vehicle storage solutions, rugged equipment mounts, and other demanding applications where reliability and performance are critical under tough conditions.

This telescopic slide is a versatile, heavy-duty solution for industries requiring robust, high-performance sliding mechanisms. With its combination of strength, smoothness, and resilience, it delivers exceptional results in the most challenging environments.

name: Stainless Steel Full Extension Super Heavy Duty Slide DS4180-080-035-0115U
description:
Product Overview

The heavy-duty telescopic slide is a premium solution designed for applications requiring exceptional load-bearing capacity and reliability. Crafted entirely from stainless steel, it offers unparalleled durability and corrosion resistance, making it suitable for use in demanding environments. With a load rating of up to 825 kg per pair, the slide is engineered for strength without compromising performance. The slide provides 100% extension, allowing full access to the drawer or platform it supports, with a maximum deflection of just 1% at the rated load.

For optimal performance, the slide should be mounted vertically; flat mounting is not recommended as it reduces the load rating by 81%. The slide supports drawer widths of up to 3,000 mm, ensuring compatibility with a wide range of designs and requirements. It operates effectively across a broad temperature range of -20 °C to 300 °C, making it suitable for diverse environments, from refrigerated storage to high-heat industrial settings. Its permitted mounting orientations include vertical and flat mounts, though vertical mounting is strongly advised for maximum capacity.

Engineered with precision, this telescopic slide delivers exceptionally smooth movement and reliable operation in the most challenging conditions, ensuring long-term performance and minimal maintenance. Its robust stainless steel construction ensures resistance to wear, impact, and harsh conditions, making it a highly versatile choice.

Applications

This telescopic slide is designed to meet the rigorous demands of specialized industries where performance, durability, and hygiene are critical:

Medical Applications: The stainless steel construction and smooth operation make this slide ideal for medical environments, where reliability and cleanability are paramount. It is suitable for use in medical equipment, diagnostic devices, and storage solutions that require robust yet precise mechanisms.

Pharmaceutical Manufacturing: The slide’s corrosion-resistant design and high load capacity make it a perfect choice for pharmaceutical manufacturing environments. It ensures smooth and reliable operation in cleanrooms or production lines, maintaining efficiency and compliance with stringent industry standards.

Marine Applications: Designed to withstand harsh environments, this slide excels in marine settings, offering corrosion resistance in saltwater conditions. It is ideal for use in shipbuilding, offshore platforms, and storage systems exposed to the elements.

Military Applications: Built for extreme durability, the slide is well-suited for military use, including vehicle storage solutions, rugged equipment mounts, and other demanding applications where reliability and performance are critical under tough conditions.

This telescopic slide is a versatile, heavy-duty solution for industries requiring robust, high-performance sliding mechanisms. With its combination of strength, smoothness, and resilience, it delivers exceptional results in the most challenging environments.

name: Stainless Steel Full Extension Super Heavy Duty Slide DS4180-080-035-0130U
description:
Product Overview

The heavy-duty telescopic slide is a premium solution designed for applications requiring exceptional load-bearing capacity and reliability. Crafted entirely from stainless steel, it offers unparalleled durability and corrosion resistance, making it suitable for use in demanding environments. With a load rating of up to 825 kg per pair, the slide is engineered for strength without compromising performance. The slide provides 100% extension, allowing full access to the drawer or platform it supports, with a maximum deflection of just 1% at the rated load.

For optimal performance, the slide should be mounted vertically; flat mounting is not recommended as it reduces the load rating by 81%. The slide supports drawer widths of up to 3,000 mm, ensuring compatibility with a wide range of designs and requirements. It operates effectively across a broad temperature range of -20 °C to 300 °C, making it suitable for diverse environments, from refrigerated storage to high-heat industrial settings. Its permitted mounting orientations include vertical and flat mounts, though vertical mounting is strongly advised for maximum capacity.

Engineered with precision, this telescopic slide delivers exceptionally smooth movement and reliable operation in the most challenging conditions, ensuring long-term performance and minimal maintenance. Its robust stainless steel construction ensures resistance to wear, impact, and harsh conditions, making it a highly versatile choice.

Applications

This telescopic slide is designed to meet the rigorous demands of specialized industries where performance, durability, and hygiene are critical:

Medical Applications: The stainless steel construction and smooth operation make this slide ideal for medical environments, where reliability and cleanability are paramount. It is suitable for use in medical equipment, diagnostic devices, and storage solutions that require robust yet precise mechanisms.

Pharmaceutical Manufacturing: The slide’s corrosion-resistant design and high load capacity make it a perfect choice for pharmaceutical manufacturing environments. It ensures smooth and reliable operation in cleanrooms or production lines, maintaining efficiency and compliance with stringent industry standards.

Marine Applications: Designed to withstand harsh environments, this slide excels in marine settings, offering corrosion resistance in saltwater conditions. It is ideal for use in shipbuilding, offshore platforms, and storage systems exposed to the elements.

Military Applications: Built for extreme durability, the slide is well-suited for military use, including vehicle storage solutions, rugged equipment mounts, and other demanding applications where reliability and performance are critical under tough conditions.

This telescopic slide is a versatile, heavy-duty solution for industries requiring robust, high-performance sliding mechanisms. With its combination of strength, smoothness, and resilience, it delivers exceptional results in the most challenging environments.

Engineered with precision, this telescopic slide delivers exceptionally smooth movement and reliable operation in the most challenging conditions, ensuring long-term performance and minimal maintenance. name: Stainless Steel Full Extension Super Heavy Duty Slide DS4180-080-035-0155U
description:
Product Overview

The heavy-duty telescopic slide is a premium solution designed for applications requiring exceptional load-bearing capacity and reliability. Crafted entirely from stainless steel, it offers unparalleled durability and corrosion resistance, making it suitable for use in demanding environments. With a load rating of up to 825 kg per pair, the slide is engineered for strength without compromising performance. The slide provides 100% extension, allowing full access to the drawer or platform it supports, with a maximum deflection of just 1% at the rated load.

For optimal performance, the slide should be mounted vertically; flat mounting is not recommended as it reduces the load rating by 81%. The slide supports drawer widths of up to 3,000 mm, ensuring compatibility with a wide range of designs and requirements. It operates effectively across a broad temperature range of -20 °C to 300 °C, making it suitable for diverse environments, from refrigerated storage to high-heat industrial settings. Its permitted mounting orientations include vertical and flat mounts, though vertical mounting is strongly advised for maximum capacity.

Engineered with precision, this telescopic slide delivers exceptionally smooth movement and reliable operation in the most challenging conditions, ensuring long-term performance and minimal maintenance. Its robust stainless steel construction ensures resistance to wear, impact, and harsh conditions, making it a highly versatile choice.

Applications

This telescopic slide is designed to meet the rigorous demands of specialized industries where performance, durability, and hygiene are critical:

Medical Applications: The stainless steel construction and smooth operation make this slide ideal for medical environments, where reliability and cleanability are paramount. It is suitable for use in medical equipment, diagnostic devices, and storage solutions that require robust yet precise mechanisms.

Pharmaceutical Manufacturing: The slide’s corrosion-resistant design and high load capacity make it a perfect choice for pharmaceutical manufacturing environments. It ensures smooth and reliable operation in cleanrooms or production lines, maintaining efficiency and compliance with stringent industry standards.

Marine Applications: Designed to withstand harsh environments, this slide excels in marine settings, offering corrosion resistance in saltwater conditions. It is ideal for use in shipbuilding, offshore platforms, and storage systems exposed to the elements.

Military Applications: Built for extreme durability, the slide is well-suited for military use, including vehicle storage solutions, rugged equipment mounts, and other demanding applications where reliability and performance are critical under tough conditions.

This telescopic slide is a versatile, heavy-duty solution for industries requiring robust, high-performance sliding mechanisms. With its combination of strength, smoothness, and resilience, it delivers exceptional results in the most challenging environments.

name: Stainless Steel Full Extension Super Heavy Duty Slide DS4180-080-035-0170U
description:
Product Overview

The heavy-duty telescopic slide is a premium solution designed for applications requiring exceptional load-bearing capacity and reliability. Crafted entirely from stainless steel, it offers unparalleled durability and corrosion resistance, making it suitable for use in demanding environments. With a load rating of up to 825 kg per pair, the slide is engineered for strength without compromising performance. The slide provides 100% extension, allowing full access to the drawer or platform it supports, with a maximum deflection of just 1% at the rated load.

For optimal performance, the slide should be mounted vertically; flat mounting is not recommended as it reduces the load rating by 81%. The slide supports drawer widths of up to 3,000 mm, ensuring compatibility with a wide range of designs and requirements. It operates effectively across a broad temperature range of -20 °C to 300 °C, making it suitable for diverse environments, from refrigerated storage to high-heat industrial settings. Its permitted mounting orientations include vertical and flat mounts, though vertical mounting is strongly advised for maximum capacity.

Engineered with precision, this telescopic slide delivers exceptionally smooth movement and reliable operation in the most challenging conditions, ensuring long-term performance and minimal maintenance. Its robust stainless steel construction ensures resistance to wear, impact, and harsh conditions, making it a highly versatile choice.

Applications

This telescopic slide is designed to meet the rigorous demands of specialized industries where performance, durability, and hygiene are critical:

Medical Applications: The stainless steel construction and smooth operation make this slide ideal for medical environments, where reliability and cleanability are paramount. It is suitable for use in medical equipment, diagnostic devices, and storage solutions that require robust yet precise mechanisms.

Pharmaceutical Manufacturing: The slide’s corrosion-resistant design and high load capacity make it a perfect choice for pharmaceutical manufacturing environments. It ensures smooth and reliable operation in cleanrooms or production lines, maintaining efficiency and compliance with stringent industry standards.

Marine Applications: Designed to withstand harsh environments, this slide excels in marine settings, offering corrosion resistance in saltwater conditions. It is ideal for use in shipbuilding, offshore platforms, and storage systems exposed to the elements.

Military Applications: Built for extreme durability, the slide is well-suited for military use, including vehicle storage solutions, rugged equipment mounts, and other demanding applications where reliability and performance are critical under tough conditions.

This telescopic slide is a versatile, heavy-duty solution for industries requiring robust, high-performance sliding mechanisms. With its combination of strength, smoothness, and resilience, it delivers exceptional results in the most challenging environments.

name: Stainless Steel Full Extension Super Heavy Duty Slide DS4180-080-035-0195U
description:
Product Overview

The heavy-duty telescopic slide is a premium solution designed for applications requiring exceptional load-bearing capacity and reliability. Crafted entirely from stainless steel, it offers unparalleled durability and corrosion resistance, making it suitable for use in demanding environments. With a load rating of up to 825 kg per pair, the slide is engineered for strength without compromising performance. The slide provides 100% extension, allowing full access to the drawer or platform it supports, with a maximum deflection of just 1% at the rated load.

For optimal performance, the slide should be mounted vertically; flat mounting is not recommended as it reduces the load rating by 81%. The slide supports drawer widths of up to 3,000 mm, ensuring compatibility with a wide range of designs and requirements. It operates effectively across a broad temperature range of -20 °C to 300 °C, making it suitable for diverse environments, from refrigerated storage to high-heat industrial settings. Its permitted mounting orientations include vertical and flat mounts, though vertical mounting is strongly advised for maximum capacity.

Engineered with precision, this telescopic slide delivers exceptionally smooth movement and reliable operation in the most challenging conditions, ensuring long-term performance and minimal maintenance. Its robust stainless steel construction ensures resistance to wear, impact, and harsh conditions, making it a highly versatile choice.

Applications

This telescopic slide is designed to meet the rigorous demands of specialized industries where performance, durability, and hygiene are critical:

Medical Applications: The stainless steel construction and smooth operation make this slide ideal for medical environments, where reliability and cleanability are paramount. It is suitable for use in medical equipment, diagnostic devices, and storage solutions that require robust yet precise mechanisms.

Pharmaceutical Manufacturing: The slide’s corrosion-resistant design and high load capacity make it a perfect choice for pharmaceutical manufacturing environments. It ensures smooth and reliable operation in cleanrooms or production lines, maintaining efficiency and compliance with stringent industry standards.

Marine Applications: Designed to withstand harsh environments, this slide excels in marine settings, offering corrosion resistance in saltwater conditions. It is ideal for use in shipbuilding, offshore platforms, and storage systems exposed to the elements.

Military Applications: Built for extreme durability, the slide is well-suited for military use, including vehicle storage solutions, rugged equipment mounts, and other demanding applications where reliability and performance are critical under tough conditions.

This telescopic slide is a versatile, heavy-duty solution for industries requiring robust, high-performance sliding mechanisms. With its combination of strength, smoothness, and resilience, it delivers exceptional results in the most challenging environments.

name: Full Extension Telescopic Slide with Lock-in Detent-out DZ5306-0030DO
description:
The DZ5306DO Redefines Strength and Precision

Experience the perfect blend of strength and precision with the DZ5306DO telescopic slide, a robust and versatile solution crafted for the most demanding industrial and heavy-duty applications. Engineered for smooth performance and long-lasting durability, this slide offers full-extension functionality, providing complete access to drawers and compartments. Its advanced design makes it ideal for environments where precision, strength, and stability are crucial.

Enhanced Safety with Dual Locking Features

This model is equipped with dual locking capabilities to enhance both safety and convenience. A hold-out feature keeps the slide securely open, maintaining a stable position during use to prevent unintended closure. Additionally, the lever-operated Lock-In mechanism holds the slide firmly shut when needed, providing stability during transport or heavy-duty operations. The intuitive lever design offers effortless control for reliable engagement and release.

High Load Capacity and Robust Performance

The DZ5306DO slide is built to handle substantial loads, supporting up to 120kg per pair. This heavy-duty capacity ensures dependable strength for demanding applications. Designed to operate reliably across a wide temperature range from -30°C to 70°C, it performs consistently even in demanding environments.

Compact Dimensions and Durable Surface Finish

With a thickness of 19.1mm and a height of 53.1mm, the slide combines a compact profile with robust strength. With a length range of 300mm to 790mm, this slide provides versatile sizing to accommodate a range of applications. Constructed from high-quality mild steel with a bright zinc finish, it offers excellent protection against wear and rust.

Common Applications and Versatility

Discover the versatility of the DZ5306DO in a range of industries:
