name: Heavy Duty Telescopic Slide with Disconnect Easy Close 400mm DZ5334-0040EC
description:
DZ5334EC Easy-Close Telescopic Slide - Precision-engineered for smooth, quiet, and reliable movement

The Accuride DZ5334-EC is a high-performance telescopic slide designed to deliver a premium user experience in both commercial and residential drawer applications. Featuring integrated Easy-Close functionality, this slide ensures drawers close smoothly and silently, enhancing both convenience and durability.

With a load rating of up to 90 kg per pair and 100% extension, the DZ5334EC is ideal for wider drawers — up to 1,000 mm — and offers full access to stored contents. Its compact 19.1 mm slide thickness allows for easy installation in space-conscious environments, while the front disconnect feature simplifies maintenance and installation.

Reliability and Performance

The DZ5334-EC guarantees smooth and reliable movement. It has been validated to 80,000 cycles at rated load (depending on the slide length). Whether in commercial settings or residential spaces, rest assured that this slide can handle the demands of your storage requirements.

The DZ5334-EC is a versatile slide designed to meet the needs of a wide range of environments. Whether in high-traffic commercial settings or demanding residential installations, it provides dependable performance with minimal maintenance.

Typical applications include:

  • Shopfitting – Ideal for retail displays, drawers, and cabinetry where reliable extension and soft-close functionality are key to user experience. Especially in applications where the visitors of the shop operate the drawers, reliability and robustness, also against misuse, are key for avoiding issues in the field.
  • Kitchens and Utility Rooms – Supports heavy drawers storing cookware, utensils, or cleaning supplies.
  • Offices and Workspaces – Perfect for filing cabinets, under-desk storage, and sliding work surfaces.
  • Tool Storage and Workshops – With its high cycle rating, it’s well-suited for tool chests, technician drawers, and mobile workstations.
  • Medical and Laboratory Equipment – Provides smooth and durable motion for storage units requiring precision and reliability.
  • Caravans and Motorhomes – Compact yet robust, ideal for maximizing storage in mobile and compact environments.

Wherever consistent performance and durability are required, the DZ5334-EC delivers.

Easy Access with Full Extension:

The full extension feature allows the user to reach the back of drawers or compartments effortlessly, enhancing convenience and practicality in your storage solutions.

Soft Close Feature:

The DZ5334-EC is designed for a smooth user experience, featuring a soft-close mechanism for the last 45 mm of the closing cycle. Enjoy smooth and quiet closure, minimizing noise and preventing abrupt slamming.

The DZ5334-EC slide is one of the few slides with a soft close feature which can function in temperatures as low as 0°C, making this slide ideal for applications like refrigerated storage or cold rooms.

Front Disconnect Feature:

For added convenience, the front disconnect feature allows easy disconnection of the slide. This makes maintenance, cleaning, and installation of the drawer hassle-free, ensuring that your storage solutions remain efficient and user-friendly.

Wide Drawers:

The DZ5334-EC can accommodate wide drawers up to one meter wide with minimized racking. We recommend that a centrally positioned handle is used on wide drawers.

Various Mounting Options:

The DZ635xx bracket accessory kit allows for side and bottom mounting options. However, please note that the DZ5334-EC telescopic slide itself is not suitable for flat mounting.
short_description: Heavy duty telescopic slide DZ5334-EC, with 100% extension, Easy-Close functionality, and a front-disconnect feature. Supports loads up to 90 kg and is ideal for wide drawers in commercial and residential applications. The slide is designed for vertical mounting and can be bottom, or platform mounted when used with the DZ635xx brackets.

name: Heavy Duty Telescopic Slide with Disconnect Easy Close 450mm DZ5334-0045EC
description:
DZ5334EC Easy-Close Telescopic Slide - Precision-engineered for smooth, quiet, and reliable movement

The Accuride DZ5334-EC is a high-performance telescopic slide designed to deliver a premium user experience in both commercial and residential drawer applications. Featuring integrated Easy-Close functionality, this slide ensures drawers close smoothly and silently, enhancing both convenience and durability.

With a load rating of up to 90 kg per pair and 100% extension, the DZ5334EC is ideal for wider drawers — up to 1,000 mm — and offers full access to stored contents. Its compact 19.1 mm slide thickness allows for easy installation in space-conscious environments, while the front disconnect feature simplifies maintenance and installation.

Reliability and Performance

The DZ5334-EC guarantees smooth and reliable movement. It has been validated to 80,000 cycles at rated load (depending on the slide length). Whether in commercial settings or residential spaces, rest assured that this slide can handle the demands of your storage requirements.

The DZ5334-EC is a versatile slide designed to meet the needs of a wide range of environments. Whether in high-traffic commercial settings or demanding residential installations, it provides dependable performance with minimal maintenance.

Typical applications include:

  • Shopfitting – Ideal for retail displays, drawers, and cabinetry where reliable extension and soft-close functionality are key to user experience. Especially in applications where the visitors of the shop operate the drawers, reliability and robustness, also against misuse, are key for avoiding issues in the field.
  • Kitchens and Utility Rooms – Supports heavy drawers storing cookware, utensils, or cleaning supplies.
  • Offices and Workspaces – Perfect for filing cabinets, under-desk storage, and sliding work surfaces.
  • Tool Storage and Workshops – With its high cycle rating, it’s well-suited for tool chests, technician drawers, and mobile workstations.
  • Medical and Laboratory Equipment – Provides smooth and durable motion for storage units requiring precision and reliability.
  • Caravans and Motorhomes – Compact yet robust, ideal for maximizing storage in mobile and compact environments.

Wherever consistent performance and durability are required, the DZ5334-EC delivers.

Easy Access with Full Extension:

The full extension feature allows the user to reach the back of drawers or compartments effortlessly, enhancing convenience and practicality in your storage solutions.

Soft Close Feature:

The DZ5334-EC is designed for a smooth user experience, featuring a soft-close mechanism for the last 45 mm of the closing cycle. Enjoy smooth and quiet closure, minimizing noise and preventing abrupt slamming.

The DZ5334-EC slide is one of the few slides with a soft close feature which can function in temperatures as low as 0°C, making this slide ideal for applications like refrigerated storage or cold rooms.

Front Disconnect Feature:

For added convenience, the front disconnect feature allows easy disconnection of the slide. This makes maintenance, cleaning, and installation of the drawer hassle-free, ensuring that your storage solutions remain efficient and user-friendly.

Wide Drawers:

The DZ5334-EC can accommodate wide drawers up to one meter wide with minimized racking. We recommend that a centrally positioned handle is used on wide drawers.

Various Mounting Options:

The DZ635xx bracket accessory kit allows for side and bottom mounting options. However, please note that the DZ5334-EC telescopic slide itself is not suitable for flat mounting.
short_description: Heavy duty telescopic slide DZ5334-EC, with 100% extension, Easy-Close functionality, and a front-disconnect feature. Supports loads up to 90 kg and is ideal for wide drawers in commercial and residential applications. The slide is designed for vertical mounting and can be bottom, or platform mounted when used with the DZ635xx brackets.

name: Heavy Duty Telescopic Slide with Disconnect Easy Close 600mm DZ5334-0060EC
description:
DZ5334EC Easy-Close Telescopic Slide - Precision-engineered for smooth, quiet, and reliable movement

The Accuride DZ5334-EC is a high-performance telescopic slide designed to deliver a premium user experience in both commercial and residential drawer applications. Featuring integrated Easy-Close functionality, this slide ensures drawers close smoothly and silently, enhancing both convenience and durability.

With a load rating of up to 90 kg per pair and 100% extension, the DZ5334EC is ideal for wider drawers — up to 1,000 mm — and offers full access to stored contents. Its compact 19.1 mm slide thickness allows for easy installation in space-conscious environments, while the front disconnect feature simplifies maintenance and installation.

Reliability and Performance

The DZ5334-EC guarantees smooth and reliable movement. It has been validated to 80,000 cycles at rated load (depending on the slide length). Whether in commercial settings or residential spaces, rest assured that this slide can handle the demands of your storage requirements.

The DZ5334-EC is a versatile slide designed to meet the needs of a wide range of environments. Whether in high-traffic commercial settings or demanding residential installations, it provides dependable performance with minimal maintenance.

Typical applications include:

  • Shopfitting – Ideal for retail displays, drawers, and cabinetry where reliable extension and soft-close functionality are key to user experience. Especially in applications where the visitors of the shop operate the drawers, reliability and robustness, also against misuse, are key for avoiding issues in the field.
  • Kitchens and Utility Rooms – Supports heavy drawers storing cookware, utensils, or cleaning supplies.
  • Offices and Workspaces – Perfect for filing cabinets, under-desk storage, and sliding work surfaces.
  • Tool Storage and Workshops – With its high cycle rating, it’s well-suited for tool chests, technician drawers, and mobile workstations.
  • Medical and Laboratory Equipment – Provides smooth and durable motion for storage units requiring precision and reliability.
  • Caravans and Motorhomes – Compact yet robust, ideal for maximizing storage in mobile and compact environments.

Wherever consistent performance and durability are required, the DZ5334-EC delivers.

Easy Access with Full Extension:

The full extension feature allows the user to reach the back of drawers or compartments effortlessly, enhancing convenience and practicality in your storage solutions.

Soft Close Feature:

The DZ5334-EC is designed for a smooth user experience, featuring a soft-close mechanism for the last 45 mm of the closing cycle. Enjoy smooth and quiet closure, minimizing noise and preventing abrupt slamming.

The DZ5334-EC slide is one of the few slides with a soft close feature which can function in temperatures as low as 0°C, making this slide ideal for applications like refrigerated storage or cold rooms.

Front Disconnect Feature:

For added convenience, the front disconnect feature allows easy disconnection of the slide. This makes maintenance, cleaning, and installation of the drawer hassle-free, ensuring that your storage solutions remain efficient and user-friendly.

Wide Drawers:

The DZ5334-EC can accommodate wide drawers up to one meter wide with minimized racking. We recommend that a centrally positioned handle is used on wide drawers.

Various Mounting Options:

The DZ635xx bracket accessory kit allows for side and bottom mounting options. However, please note that the DZ5334-EC telescopic slide itself is not suitable for flat mounting.
short_description: Heavy duty telescopic slide DZ5334-EC, with 100% extension, Easy-Close functionality, and a front-disconnect feature. Supports loads up to 90 kg and is ideal for wide drawers in commercial and residential applications. The slide is designed for vertical mounting and can be bottom, or platform mounted when used with the DZ635xx brackets.

description:

name: Soft Close Drawer Slide DB3832-0065EC-D
description:
The DB3832-EC-D Black Finish EasyClose Slide: Ideal for Office, Kitchen, and Retail Use

The DB3832-EC-D is a black zinc finish light-duty drawer slide engineered for enhanced strength and smooth, reliable motion. Designed with a load capacity of up to 45 kg per pair and full 100% extension, it features a front lever disconnect mechanism for easy installation and maintenance.

Its compact 12.7 mm slide thickness (14 mm with mounting bracket) allows for easy installation in cabinet hardware applications, while the front disconnect feature simplifies its maintenance.

 

Reliability and Performance:

The silent operation of the DB3832-EC-D ensures smooth, quiet sliding, ideal for noise-sensitive environments. For added versatility, an optional clip-on bracket is available to support both bottom and platform mounting configurations of the slide.

Typical applications include:

  • Offices and Workspaces - With its high cycle rating of 80,000, it’s well-suited for a wide variety of pull-out shelves, e.g. filing cabinets, under-desk storage, and sliding work surfaces.
  • Kitchens and Utility Rooms – Offers durable, smooth motion, making it perfect for residential applications, and a sleek black finish to match dark cabinetry such as utensil drawers, cookware storage, or cleaning supply cabinets.
  • Point-of-Sale Trays – A great solution for retail cabinetry where reliable extension, a sleek look, and soft-close functionality are key to user experience.

Black Zinc Finish

The DB3832-EC-D is a sleek black version of the 3800 series slide with easy close. This new finish offers a modern look with enhanced design versatility - perfect for matching dark cabinetry, high-end retail fixtures, or contemporary office furniture.

With the same trusted performance and features as the standard model, the black version combines aesthetic appeal with quiet, reliable functionality.

Hold-In Detent:

The EasyClose Mechanism also acts like a hold-in detent and prevents roll-out and/or bounce back in closed position.

Soft Close Feature:

The DB3832-EC-D is designed for a smooth user experience, featuring a soft-close mechanism. Enjoy smooth and quiet closure, minimising noise and preventing abrupt slamming.

Front Disconnect Feature:

For added convenience, the front-disconnect functionality makes drawer removal and reinsertion quick and easy, simplifying installation, maintenance, and cleaning tasks.

Cam Drawer Adjust:

Our Cam Drawer Adjust feature allows for up to 3.2 mm of vertical adjustment, ensuring a perfect fit and smooth operation.

name: Black Full Extension Slide with Easy Close DB4501-0020EC
description:
Full Extension Slide with Easy Close DB4501-EC

Introducing the DB4501-EC Full Extension Slide with Easy Close, designed to provide reliability and durability for various soft close applications. Engineered for 100% full extension, this slide offers easy access to previously unused drawer space, ensuring every inch of your storage is utilised efficiently. Available in slide lengths ranging from 200 mm to 600 mm, the DB4501-EC caters to a range of applications.

Easy Close Mechanism:

The DB4501-EC slide features an integrated easy close system, eliminating loud slamming and ensuring a quiet, gentle closure. This makes it ideal for noise-sensitive environments.

Full Extension :

Designed with a 100% full extension feature, the DB4501-EC telescopic slide allows complete access to the entire drawer, making it perfect for storage spaces where reaching the back is important.

Easy Installation:

The front disconnect feature simplifies installation and maintenance, enabling easy detachment when necessary.

Black Zinc Finish

The DB4501-EC is a sleek black version of the 4501 series slide with easy close. This new finish offers a modern look with enhanced design versatility. With the same trusted performance and features as the standard model, the black version combines aesthetic appeal with quiet, reliable functionality.

Ideal Applications

The DB4501-EC easy close slide is perfect for a wide range of applications, including:

  • Vending Machines: Ensures quiet and smooth operation.
  • Retail Storage: Provides secure and gentle closure, protecting delicate items.
  • Under Bed Storage Drawers: Maximises space utilisation with full extension and silent operation.

name: Black Full Extension Slide with Touch Release DB4501-0020TR
description:
The DB4501-TR Full Extension Slide with Touch Release

The DB4501-TR Full Extension Slide with Touch Release is a premium sliding solution designed for optimal performance and convenience. Constructed from mild steel, this slide has a sleek black zinc finish.

Innovative Touch to Release Mechanism

One of the standout features of the DB4501-TR telescopic slide is the touch-to-release (touch to open/ push to open) mechanism. This eliminates the need for handles, contributing to sleek and modern cabinetry designs, ensuring that the drawer opens effortlessly with a simple touch.

Black Zinc Finish

The DB4501-TR is a sleek black version of the 4501 series slide with touch release. This new finish offers a modern look with enhanced design versatility. With the same trusted performance and features as the standard model, the black version combines aesthetic appeal with quiet, reliable functionality.

Slide Installation

Key features of this slide include a disconnect mechanism that simplifies installation. Additionally, the DB4501-TR slide is equipped with breathing tabs, designed to facilitate straightforward installation, ensuring a perfect fit every time.

Hold-in Feature

The hold-in feature guarantees that the drawer remains securely shut, enhancing safety and stability.

100% Extension Feature

Engineered to provide 100% full extension, the DB4501-TR slide ensures easy access to the back of the drawer, making it perfect for a variety of applications.
short_description: The DB4501-TR Full Extension Slide has been designed with touch-to-release, disconnect and hold-in features. With a load rating of up to 35 kg and a black finish, the slide is ideal for matching dark cabinetry, high-end retail fixtures, or contemporary furniture.
product_features:
• Front lever disconnect for easy installation and maintenance.
  • Breathing tabs for straightforward installation, ensuring a perfect fit every time.
  • Hold-in feature to ensure the drawer stays closed until an additional force is applied.
  • Push to open/touch release function offers seamless performance, ensuring that the drawer opens effortlessly with a simple touch.
  • Accuride International Limited guarantees its “Quick Ship”™ slides against defects in material and workmanship. Please read more under the quality and warranty policy section.

name: Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide DZ4180-060-032-0050U
description:
DZ4180-060-032 Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide

The Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide is a robust, high-performance slide designed for use in tight spaces without sacrificing load capacity. Engineered with a slim I-beam profile, it provides support in a more compact footprint than others in the 4180 series.

Reliability and Performance

With a load rating of up to 622kg per pair and 100% extension, this slide ensures unrestricted access to heavy components while maintaining structural integrity under demanding conditions. High corrosion resistance, verified through 220 hours of salt spray testing, provides smooth and reliable performance across a wide range of conditions and temperatures, from -20 °C to 110 °C.

Applications

  • Laboratory and Research Equipment: Its compact profile allows for integration into confined spaces such as laboratory cabinets, analytical instruments, and medical testing platforms.
  • Military Applications: Designed for extreme durability, this slide delivers reliable performance in military applications, i.e. in vehicle storage solutions and equipment mounts.
  • Marine Applications: Engineered for tough conditions, this slide resists corrosion effectively and performs reliably in saltwater environments.

Slim I-Beam Profile

The integrated I-beam design enhances rigidity without increasing the slide’s width, making it ideal for installations where space is limited but mechanical strength cannot be compromised.

100% Extension for Complete Access

The slide offers full extension, ensuring total visibility and reach into drawers, platforms, or components.

Compatible with DBHAND Locking Mechanism

Safety and convenience are enhanced through compatibility with the DBHAND locking system. This ensures secure retention of the slide, preventing accidental movement during use or transport.

Corrosion Resistant

The slide delivers long-lasting durability. Its resistance to rust and surface degradation makes it suitable for both industrial and marine environments.
short_description: The DZ4180-060-032 is a compact, heavy-duty slide engineered for demanding environments with a high load rating of up to 622kg per pair, 100% extension and 1% deflection. Offering high corrosion resistance and long-term durability in harsh conditions, this slide is ideal for military, marine and laboratory applications.
product_features:
• I-beam intermediate member for extra strength
  • Accuride International Limited guarantees its “Quick Ship”™ slides against defects in material and workmanship. Please read more under quality and warranty policy section.

name: Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide DZ4180-060-032-0060U
description:
DZ4180-060-032 Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide

The Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide is a robust, high-performance slide designed for use in tight spaces without sacrificing load capacity. Engineered with a slim I-beam profile, it provides support in a more compact footprint than others in the 4180 series.

Reliability and Performance

With a load rating of up to 622kg per pair and 100% extension, this slide ensures unrestricted access to heavy components while maintaining structural integrity under demanding conditions. High corrosion resistance, verified through 220 hours of salt spray testing, provides smooth and reliable performance across a wide range of conditions and temperatures, from -20 °C to 110 °C.

Applications

  • Laboratory and Research Equipment: Its compact profile allows for integration into confined spaces such as laboratory cabinets, analytical instruments, and medical testing platforms.
  • Military Applications: Designed for extreme durability, this slide delivers reliable performance in military applications, i.e. in vehicle storage solutions and equipment mounts.
  • Marine Applications: Engineered for tough conditions, this slide resists corrosion effectively and performs reliably in saltwater environments.

Slim I-Beam Profile

The integrated I-beam design enhances rigidity without increasing the slide’s width, making it ideal for installations where space is limited but mechanical strength cannot be compromised.

100% Extension for Complete Access

The slide offers full extension, ensuring total visibility and reach into drawers, platforms, or components.

Compatible with DBHAND Locking Mechanism

Safety and convenience are enhanced through compatibility with the DBHAND locking system. This ensures secure retention of the slide, preventing accidental movement during use or transport.

Corrosion Resistant

The slide delivers long-lasting durability. Its resistance to rust and surface degradation makes it suitable for both industrial and marine environments.
short_description: The DZ4180-060-032 is a compact, heavy-duty slide engineered for demanding environments with a high load rating of up to 622kg per pair, 100% extension and 1% deflection. Offering high corrosion resistance and long-term durability in harsh conditions, this slide is ideal for military, marine and laboratory applications.

name: Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide DZ4180-060-032-0075U
description:
DZ4180-060-032 Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide

The Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide is a robust, high-performance slide designed for use in tight spaces without sacrificing load capacity. Engineered with a slim I-beam profile, it provides support in a more compact footprint than others in the 4180 series.

Reliability and Performance

With a load rating of up to 622kg per pair and 100% extension, this slide ensures unrestricted access to heavy components while maintaining structural integrity under demanding conditions. High corrosion resistance, verified through 220 hours of salt spray testing, provides smooth and reliable performance across a wide range of conditions and temperatures, from -20 °C to 110 °C.

Applications

  • Laboratory and Research Equipment: Its compact profile allows for integration into confined spaces such as laboratory cabinets, analytical instruments, and medical testing platforms.
  • Military Applications: Designed for extreme durability, this slide delivers reliable performance in military applications, i.e. in vehicle storage solutions and equipment mounts.
  • Marine Applications: Engineered for tough conditions, this slide resists corrosion effectively and performs reliably in saltwater environments.

Slim I-Beam Profile

The integrated I-beam design enhances rigidity without increasing the slide’s width, making it ideal for installations where space is limited but mechanical strength cannot be compromised.

100% Extension for Complete Access

The slide offers full extension, ensuring total visibility and reach into drawers, platforms, or components.

Compatible with DBHAND Locking Mechanism

Safety and convenience are enhanced through compatibility with the DBHAND locking system. This ensures secure retention of the slide, preventing accidental movement during use or transport.

Corrosion Resistant

The slide delivers long-lasting durability. Its resistance to rust and surface degradation makes it suitable for both industrial and marine environments.
short_description: The DZ4180-060-032 is a compact, heavy-duty slide engineered for demanding environments with a high load rating of up to 622kg per pair, 100% extension and 1% deflection. Offering high corrosion resistance and long-term durability in harsh conditions, this slide is ideal for military, marine and laboratory applications.

name: Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide DZ4180-060-032-0090U
description:
DZ4180-060-032 Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide

The Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide is a robust, high-performance slide designed for use in tight spaces without sacrificing load capacity. Engineered with a slim I-beam profile, it provides support in a more compact footprint than others in the 4180 series.

Reliability and Performance

With a load rating of up to 622kg per pair and 100% extension, this slide ensures unrestricted access to heavy components while maintaining structural integrity under demanding conditions. High corrosion resistance, verified through 220 hours of salt spray testing, provides smooth and reliable performance across a wide range of conditions and temperatures, from -20 °C to 110 °C.

Applications

  • Laboratory and Research Equipment: Its compact profile allows for integration into confined spaces such as laboratory cabinets, analytical instruments, and medical testing platforms.
  • Military Applications: Designed for extreme durability, this slide delivers reliable performance in military applications, i.e. in vehicle storage solutions and equipment mounts.
  • Marine Applications: Engineered for tough conditions, this slide resists corrosion effectively and performs reliably in saltwater environments.

Slim I-Beam Profile

The integrated I-beam design enhances rigidity without increasing the slide’s width, making it ideal for installations where space is limited but mechanical strength cannot be compromised.

100% Extension for Complete Access

The slide offers full extension, ensuring total visibility and reach into drawers, platforms, or components.

Compatible with DBHAND Locking Mechanism

Safety and convenience are enhanced through compatibility with the DBHAND locking system. This ensures secure retention of the slide, preventing accidental movement during use or transport.

Corrosion Resistant

The slide delivers long-lasting durability. Its resistance to rust and surface degradation makes it suitable for both industrial and marine environments.
short_description: The DZ4180-060-032 is a compact, heavy-duty slide engineered for demanding environments with a high load rating of up to 622kg per pair, 100% extension and 1% deflection. Offering high corrosion resistance and long-term durability in harsh conditions, this slide is ideal for military, marine and laboratory applications.

name: Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide DZ4180-060-032-0105U
description:
DZ4180-060-032 Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide

The Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide is a robust, high-performance slide designed for use in tight spaces without sacrificing load capacity. Engineered with a slim I-beam profile, it provides support in a more compact footprint than others in the 4180 series.

Reliability and Performance

With a load rating of up to 622kg per pair and 100% extension, this slide ensures unrestricted access to heavy components while maintaining structural integrity under demanding conditions. High corrosion resistance, verified through 220 hours of salt spray testing, provides smooth and reliable performance across a wide range of conditions and temperatures, from -20 °C to 110 °C.

Applications

  • Laboratory and Research Equipment: Its compact profile allows for integration into confined spaces such as laboratory cabinets, analytical instruments, and medical testing platforms.
  • Military Applications: Designed for extreme durability, this slide delivers reliable performance in military applications, i.e. in vehicle storage solutions and equipment mounts.
  • Marine Applications: Engineered for tough conditions, this slide resists corrosion effectively and performs reliably in saltwater environments.

Slim I-Beam Profile

The integrated I-beam design enhances rigidity without increasing the slide’s width, making it ideal for installations where space is limited but mechanical strength cannot be compromised.

100% Extension for Complete Access

The slide offers full extension, ensuring total visibility and reach into drawers, platforms, or components.

Compatible with DBHAND Locking Mechanism

Safety and convenience are enhanced through compatibility with the DBHAND locking system. This ensures secure retention of the slide, preventing accidental movement during use or transport.

Corrosion Resistant

The slide delivers long-lasting durability. Its resistance to rust and surface degradation makes it suitable for both industrial and marine environments.
short_description: The DZ4180-060-032 is a compact, heavy-duty slide engineered for demanding environments with a high load rating of up to 622kg per pair, 100% extension and 1% deflection. Offering high corrosion resistance and long-term durability in harsh conditions, this slide is ideal for military, marine and laboratory applications.
product_features:
• I-beam intermediate member for extra strength
  • Accuride International Limited guarantees its “Quick Ship”™ slides against defects in material and workmanship. Please read more under quality and warranty policy section.

name: Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide DZ4180-060-032-0120U
description:
DZ4180-060-032 Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide

The Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide is a robust, high-performance slide designed for use in tight spaces without sacrificing load capacity. Engineered with a slim I-beam profile, it provides support in a more compact footprint than others in the 4180 series.

Reliability and Performance

With a load rating of up to 622kg per pair and 100% extension, this slide ensures unrestricted access to heavy components while maintaining structural integrity under demanding conditions. High corrosion resistance, verified through 220 hours of salt spray testing, provides smooth and reliable performance across a wide range of conditions and temperatures, from -20 °C to 110 °C.

Applications

  • Laboratory and Research Equipment: Its compact profile allows for integration into confined spaces such as laboratory cabinets, analytical instruments, and medical testing platforms.
  • Military Applications: Designed for extreme durability, this slide delivers reliable performance in military applications, i.e. in vehicle storage solutions and equipment mounts.
  • Marine Applications: Engineered for tough conditions, this slide resists corrosion effectively and performs reliably in saltwater environments.

Slim I-Beam Profile

The integrated I-beam design enhances rigidity without increasing the slide’s width, making it ideal for installations where space is limited but mechanical strength cannot be compromised.

100% Extension for Complete Access

The slide offers full extension, ensuring total visibility and reach into drawers, platforms, or components.

Compatible with DBHAND Locking Mechanism

Safety and convenience are enhanced through compatibility with the DBHAND locking system. This ensures secure retention of the slide, preventing accidental movement during use or transport.

Corrosion Resistant

The slide delivers long-lasting durability. Its resistance to rust and surface degradation makes it suitable for both industrial and marine environments.
short_description: The DZ4180-060-032 is a compact, heavy-duty slide engineered for demanding environments with a high load rating of up to 622kg per pair, 100% extension and 1% deflection. Offering high corrosion resistance and long-term durability in harsh conditions, this slide is ideal for military, marine and laboratory applications.
product_features:
• I-beam intermediate member for extra strength
  • Accuride International Limited guarantees its “Quick Ship”™ slides against defects in material and workmanship. Please read more under quality and warranty policy section.

name: Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide DZ4180-060-032-0135U
description:
DZ4180-060-032 Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide

The Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide is a robust, high-performance slide designed for use in tight spaces without sacrificing load capacity. Engineered with a slim I-beam profile, it provides support in a more compact footprint than others in the 4180 series.

Reliability and Performance

With a load rating of up to 622kg per pair and 100% extension, this slide ensures unrestricted access to heavy components while maintaining structural integrity under demanding conditions. High corrosion resistance, verified through 220 hours of salt spray testing, provides smooth and reliable performance across a wide range of conditions and temperatures, from -20 °C to 110 °C.

Applications

  • Laboratory and Research Equipment: Its compact profile allows for integration into confined spaces such as laboratory cabinets, analytical instruments, and medical testing platforms.
  • Military Applications: Designed for extreme durability, this slide delivers reliable performance in military applications, i.e. in vehicle storage solutions and equipment mounts.
  • Marine Applications: Engineered for tough conditions, this slide resists corrosion effectively and performs reliably in saltwater environments.

Slim I-Beam Profile

The integrated I-beam design enhances rigidity without increasing the slide’s width, making it ideal for installations where space is limited but mechanical strength cannot be compromised.

100% Extension for Complete Access

The slide offers full extension, ensuring total visibility and reach into drawers, platforms, or components.

Compatible with DBHAND Locking Mechanism

Safety and convenience are enhanced through compatibility with the DBHAND locking system. This ensures secure retention of the slide, preventing accidental movement during use or transport.

Corrosion Resistant

The slide delivers long-lasting durability. Its resistance to rust and surface degradation makes it suitable for both industrial and marine environments.
short_description: The DZ4180-060-032 is a compact, heavy-duty slide engineered for demanding environments with a high load rating of up to 622kg per pair, 100% extension and 1% deflection. Offering high corrosion resistance and long-term durability in harsh conditions, this slide is ideal for military, marine and laboratory applications.

name: Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide DZ4180-060-032-0150U
description:
DZ4180-060-032 Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide

The Compact Heavy-Duty Telescopic Slide is a robust, high-performance slide designed for use in tight spaces without sacrificing load capacity. Engineered with a slim I-beam profile, it provides support in a more compact footprint than others in the 4180 series.

Reliability and Performance

With a load rating of up to 622kg per pair and 100% extension, this slide ensures unrestricted access to heavy components while maintaining structural integrity under demanding conditions. High corrosion resistance, verified through 220 hours of salt spray testing, provides smooth and reliable performance across a wide range of conditions and temperatures, from -20 °C to 110 °C.

Applications

  • Laboratory and Research Equipment: Its compact profile allows for integration into confined spaces such as laboratory cabinets, analytical instruments, and medical testing platforms.
  • Military Applications: Designed for extreme durability, this slide delivers reliable performance in military applications, i.e. in vehicle storage solutions and equipment mounts.
  • Marine Applications: Engineered for tough conditions, this slide resists corrosion effectively and performs reliably in saltwater environments.

Slim I-Beam Profile

The integrated I-beam design enhances rigidity without increasing the slide’s width, making it ideal for installations where space is limited but mechanical strength cannot be compromised.

100% Extension for Complete Access

The slide offers full extension, ensuring total visibility and reach into drawers, platforms, or components.

Compatible with DBHAND Locking Mechanism

Safety and convenience are enhanced through compatibility with the DBHAND locking system. This ensures secure retention of the slide, preventing accidental movement during use or transport.

Corrosion Resistant

The slide delivers long-lasting durability. Its resistance to rust and surface degradation makes it suitable for both industrial and marine environments.
short_description: The DZ4180-060-032 is a compact, heavy-duty slide engineered for demanding environments with a high load rating of up to 622kg per pair, 100% extension and 1% deflection. Offering high corrosion resistance and long-term durability in harsh conditions, this slide is ideal for military, marine and laboratory applications.

name: Full Extension Telescopic Slide with Lock-in Detent-out DZ5306-0030DO
description:
The DZ5306-DO Redefines Strength and Precision

Experience the perfect blend of strength and precision with the DZ5306-DO telescopic slide, a robust and versatile solution crafted for the most demanding industrial and heavy-duty applications. Engineered for smooth performance and long-lasting durability, this slide offers full-extension functionality, providing complete access to drawers and compartments. Its advanced design makes it ideal for environments where precision, strength, and stability are crucial.

Enhanced Safety with Dual Locking Features

This model is equipped with dual locking capabilities to enhance both safety and convenience. A hold-out feature keeps the slide securely open, maintaining a stable position during use to prevent unintended closure. Additionally, the lever-operated Lock-In mechanism holds the slide firmly shut when needed, providing stability during transport or heavy-duty operations. The intuitive lever design offers effortless control for reliable engagement and release.

High Load Capacity and Robust Performance

The DZ5306-DO slide is built to handle substantial loads, supporting up to 120kg per pair. This heavy-duty capacity ensures dependable strength for demanding applications. Designed to operate reliably across a wide temperature range from -30°C to 70°C, it performs consistently even in demanding environments.

Compact Dimensions and Durable Surface Finish

With a thickness of 19.1mm and a height of 53.1mm, the slide combines a compact profile with robust strength. With a length range of 300mm to 1100 mm, this slide provides versatile sizing to accommodate a range of applications. Constructed from high-quality mild steel with a bright zinc finish, it offers excellent protection against wear and rust.

Common Applications and Versatility

Discover the versatility of the DZ5306-DO in a range of industries:

  • Van racking systems: Enhances vehicle organization by securing tools and heavy equipment. The slide’s reliable locking mechanisms keep drawers in place during transit, boosting safety while allowing easy access to contents when stationary.
  • Industrial storage: Improves efficiency in tool compartments, display cabinets, and compact warehouses with full-extension access and robust performance.
  • Emergency service vehicles: Enhances safety and quick access for essential tools and equipment, keeping drawers securely locked during transport and easily accessible in critical moments.

Take control of your storage with the DZ5306-DO full-extension slide. Enjoy smooth operation, reliable locking and high load capacity—all in one durable design.

For detailed dimensions and additional information, refer to the product's datasheet or reach out to us directly for personalized assistance.

name: Full Extension Telescopic Slide with Lock-in Detent-out DZ5306-0050DO
description:
The DZ5306-DO Redefines Strength and Precision

Experience the perfect blend of strength and precision with the DZ5306-DO telescopic slide, a robust and versatile solution crafted for the most demanding industrial and heavy-duty applications. Engineered for smooth performance and long-lasting durability, this slide offers full-extension functionality, providing complete access to drawers and compartments. Its advanced design makes it ideal for environments where precision, strength, and stability are crucial.

Enhanced Safety with Dual Locking Features

This model is equipped with dual locking capabilities to enhance both safety and convenience. A hold-out feature keeps the slide securely open, maintaining a stable position during use to prevent unintended closure. Additionally, the lever-operated Lock-In mechanism holds the slide firmly shut when needed, providing stability during transport or heavy-duty operations. The intuitive lever design offers effortless control for reliable engagement and release.

High Load Capacity and Robust Performance

The DZ5306-DO slide is built to handle substantial loads, supporting up to 120kg per pair. This heavy-duty capacity ensures dependable strength for demanding applications. Designed to operate reliably across a wide temperature range from -30°C to 70°C, it performs consistently even in demanding environments.

Compact Dimensions and Durable Surface Finish

With a thickness of 19.1mm and a height of 53.1mm, the slide combines a compact profile with robust strength. With a length range of 300mm to 1100 mm, this slide provides versatile sizing to accommodate a range of applications. Constructed from high-quality mild steel with a bright zinc finish, it offers excellent protection against wear and rust.

Common Applications and Versatility

Discover the versatility of the DZ5306-DO in a range of industries:

  • Van racking systems: Enhances vehicle organization by securing tools and heavy equipment. The slide’s reliable locking mechanisms keep drawers in place during transit, boosting safety while allowing easy access to contents when stationary.
  • Industrial storage: Improves efficiency in tool compartments, display cabinets, and compact warehouses with full-extension access and robust performance.
  • Emergency service vehicles: Enhances safety and quick access for essential tools and equipment, keeping drawers securely locked during transport and easily accessible in critical moments.

Take control of your storage with the DZ5306-DO full-extension slide. Enjoy smooth operation, reliable locking and high load capacity—all in one durable design.

For detailed dimensions and additional information, refer to the product's datasheet or reach out to us directly for personalized assistance.

name: Full Extension Telescopic Slide with Lock-in Detent-out DZ5306-0080DO
description:
The DZ5306-DO Redefines Strength and Precision

Experience the perfect blend of strength and precision with the DZ5306-DO telescopic slide, a robust and versatile solution crafted for the most demanding industrial and heavy-duty applications. Engineered for smooth performance and long-lasting durability, this slide offers full-extension functionality, providing complete access to drawers and compartments. Its advanced design makes it ideal for environments where precision, strength, and stability are crucial.

Enhanced Safety with Dual Locking Features

This model is equipped with dual locking capabilities to enhance both safety and convenience. A hold-out feature keeps the slide securely open, maintaining a stable position during use to prevent unintended closure. Additionally, the lever-operated Lock-In mechanism holds the slide firmly shut when needed, providing stability during transport or heavy-duty operations. The intuitive lever design offers effortless control for reliable engagement and release.

High Load Capacity and Robust Performance

The DZ5306-DO slide is built to handle substantial loads, supporting up to 120kg per pair. This heavy-duty capacity ensures dependable strength for demanding applications. Designed to operate reliably across a wide temperature range from -30°C to 70°C, it performs consistently even in demanding environments.

Compact Dimensions and Durable Surface Finish

With a thickness of 19.1mm and a height of 53.1mm, the slide combines a compact profile with robust strength. With a length range of 300mm to 1100 mm, this slide provides versatile sizing to accommodate a range of applications. Constructed from high-quality mild steel with a bright zinc finish, it offers excellent protection against wear and rust.

Common Applications and Versatility

Discover the versatility of the DZ5306-DO in a range of industries:

  • Van racking systems: Enhances vehicle organization by securing tools and heavy equipment. The slide’s reliable locking mechanisms keep drawers in place during transit, boosting safety while allowing easy access to contents when stationary.
  • Industrial storage: Improves efficiency in tool compartments, display cabinets, and compact warehouses with full-extension access and robust performance.
  • Emergency service vehicles: Enhances safety and quick access for essential tools and equipment, keeping drawers securely locked during transport and easily accessible in critical moments.

Take control of your storage with the DZ5306-DO full-extension slide. Enjoy smooth operation, reliable locking and high load capacity—all in one durable design.

For detailed dimensions and additional information, refer to the product's datasheet or reach out to us directly for personalized assistance.

  • Industrial storage: Improves efficiency in tool compartments, display cabinets, and compact warehouses with full-extension access and robust performance.
  • Emergency service vehicles: Enhances safety and quick access for essential tools and equipment, keeping drawers securely locked during transport and easily accessible in critical moments.

Take control of your storage with the DZ5306-DO full-extension slide. Enjoy smooth operation, reliable locking and high load capacity—all in one durable design.

For detailed dimensions and additional information, refer to the product's datasheet or reach out to us directly for personalized assistance.
short_description: The DZ5306-DO telescopic slide delivers full-extension functionality with a durable design supporting up to 120 kg per pair. Equipped with a hold-out feature to maintain an open position and a lever-operated Lock-In mechanism for secure closure, it offers enhanced safety and stability. This slide is an excellent choice for applications requiring strength, precision, and dependable performance.
product_features:
• Left and right levers can be connected with horizontal bar if needed
  • Use as pair or with DZ5321 as companion slide
  • Lock-in operated by lever
  • Hold-out
